    <h1 class="cs-h2" style="font-size: clamp(32px, 5vw, 56px); max-width: 900px;">Reducing Checkout Friction After Renters Are Ready to Book</h1>
    <p class="cs-hero-sub">Checkout is the commitment phase. The redesign protected that moment by resolving identity earlier, keeping order-critical tasks in checkout, and moving nonessential prompts after purchase.</p>

