    <h2 class="cs-h2">Checkout is the commitment layer of the marketplace journey</h2>
    <p class="cs-lead">Every earlier stage of the journey is about deciding. Checkout is the one stage where the user has already decided &mdash; and the interface should treat that differently.</p>

    <div class="cs-journey-grid">
      <div class="cs-journey-item">
