  <section id="design" class="cs-section container">
    <div class="cs-kicker">03 &mdash; DESIGN</div>
    <h2 class="cs-h2">Solutions across the three checkout jobs</h2>

    <div class="cs-solutions">
      <div>
        <div class="cs-solution-head">
          <h3><span class="cs-solution-num">1 &middot;</span> Resolve identity earlier</h3>
          <p>Removed the guest/password split and moved to OTP verification &mdash; preventing existing-email, password-mismatch, and password-rule errors, and avoiding late password creation that could cost users their progress.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="cs-media" style="aspect-ratio: 21 / 9">
          <img class="modal-target" src="mockup_desktop1.png" alt="Sign up / log in — identity resolved before checkout" data-modal-gallery="checkout-solution-identity">
        </div>
      </div>

      <div>
        <div class="cs-solution-head">
          <h3><span class="cs-solution-num">2 &middot;</span> Make checkout reviewable and focused</h3>
          <p>One-page checkout with section-by-section validation: completed sections collapse, errors surface in context, and the final review happens before placing the order &mdash; not after a surprise.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="cs-media" style="aspect-ratio: 21 / 9">
          <img class="modal-target" src="mockup_desktop2.png" alt="Main checkout — one page, section validation, collapsible sections" data-modal-gallery="checkout-solution-review">
        </div>
      </div>

      <div>
        <div class="cs-solution-head">
          <h3><span class="cs-solution-num">3 &middot;</span> Move nonessential tasks out</h3>
          <p>Survey and app-download prompts moved to the confirmation page; trip and cart editing minimized inside checkout; the footer reduced so the order is the only remaining task.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="cs-media" style="aspect-ratio: 21 / 9">
          <img class="modal-target" src="mockup_desktop3.png" alt="Post-checkout — survey and app prompts on confirmation" data-modal-gallery="checkout-solution-focus">
        </div>
      </div>

      <div>
        <div class="cs-solution-head">
          <div class="cs-kicker" style="margin-bottom: 12px">CROSS-PLATFORM ADAPTATION</div>
          <h3 style="margin-bottom: 0">Collapse without hiding</h3>
          <p>On mobile, completed sections collapsed to reduce scrolling while preserving review and access to the final action, with a sticky completion CTA in the review state.</p>
        </div>
