        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="cs-pullquote">
      <p>Checkout was a high-value commitment moment. The redesign protected it by <span class="accent">resolving identity earlier, making checkout reviewable, and moving nonessential tasks out</span>.</p>
